---
title: Honeyed Halloumi Ciabatta Ready in 10 | Three Steps
description: We’ve drizzled halloumi in sweet and sticky honey to create a centrepiece for our ciabatta that’ll knock your socks off. Stacked on top of sundried tomato mayonnaise and served with a refreshing tomato & rocket salad and diced potatoes, this super simple recipe 10 minute recipe is an instant winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honeyed-halloumi-ciabatta-cb33fc4e-e99f4737.jpg
